headline: Bio-Techne Q1 Earnings Preview: What's in Store for the Stock?
summary: TECH's Q1 results could reflect steady Protein Sciences growth but pressure in Spatial Biology amid NIH and biotech funding uncertainty.

headline: ScaleReady Announces multiple G-Rex® Grants have been awarded to leading investigators at Children's National Hospital
summary: ScaleReady, in collaboration with Wilson Wolf Manufacturing, Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ: TECH) and CellReady, announced four G-Rex Grants have been awarded to faculty members at Children's National Hospital. The funding, totaling $375,000, will support the optimization and translation of various cell and gene therapy initiatives into the clinic.
